122,052", "bbox": [643.8, 826.6, 830.4, 849.8]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [852.1, 826.7, 862.5, 849.8]}, {"text": "3,671", "bbox": [881.5, 826.7, 928.3, 849.8]}, {"text": "$1,734,303", "bbox": [950.0, 826.7, 1045.0, 849.8]}, {"text": "$ 1,438,445", "bbox": [1066.7, 826.7, 1163.7, 849.8]}, {"text": "Term Asset-Backed Securitization VIEs", "bbox": [104.2, 870.8, 430.0, 893.9]}, {"text": "The Company transfers U.S. retail motorcycle finance receivables to SPEs which in turn issue secured notes to investors,", "bbox": [154.2, 914.6, 1168.5, 937.6]}, {"text": "with various maturities and interest rates, secured by future collections of the purchased U.S. retail motorcycle finance", "bbox": [104.2, 939.6, 1097.0, 962.6]}, {"text": "receivables. Each term asset-backed securitization SPE is a separate legal entity and the U.S. retail motorcycle finance", "bbox": [104.2, 964.6, 1095.8, 987.6]}, {"text": "receivables included in the term asset-backed securitizations are only available for payment of the secured debt and other", "bbox": [104.2, 989.6, 1119.0, 1012.6]}, {"text": "obligations arising from the term asset-backed securitization transactions and are not available to pay other obligations or", "bbox": [104.2, 1014.6, 1120.8, 1037.6]}, {"text": "claims of the Company’s creditors until the associated secured debt and other obligations are satisfied. There are no", "bbox": [104.2, 1039.6, 1071.7, 1062.6]}, {"text": "amortization schedules for the secured notes; however, the debt is reduced monthly as available collections on the related U.S.", "bbox": [104.2, 1064.6, 1162.1, 1087.6]}, {"text": "retail motorcycle finance receivables are applied to outstanding principal. Restricted cash balances held by the SPEs are used", "bbox": [104.2, 1089.6, 1152.0, 1112.6]}, {"text": "only to support the securitizations.", "bbox": [104.2, 1114.6, 397.0, 1137.6]}, {"text": "In 2015, the Company transferred a total of $1.31 billion of U.S. retail motorcycle finance receivables to two separate", "bbox": [154.2, 1158.3, 1140.6, 1181.4]}, {"text": "SPEs. The SPEs in turn issued $1.20 billion of secured notes. In 2014, the Company transferred $924.9 million of U.S. retail", "bbox": [104.2, 1183.3, 1147.7, 1206.4]}, {"text": "motorcycle finance receivables to one SPE. The SPE in turn issued $850.0 million of secured notes. At December 31, 2015, the", "bbox": [104.2, 1208.3, 1170.7, 1231.4]}, {"text": "Company's consolidated balance sheet included outstanding balances related to the following secured notes with the related", "bbox": [104.2, 1233.3, 1139.0, 1256.4]}, {"text": "maturity dates and interest rates (in thousands):", "bbox": [104.2, 1258.3, 503.4, 1281.4]}, {"text": "Issue Date", "bbox": [254.8, 1333.4, 328.4, 1351.9]}, {"text": "Principal", "bbox": [535.8, 1300.4, 601.6, 1318.9]}, {"text": "Amount at Date of", "bbox": [502.7, 1317.1, 638.8, 1335.5]}, {"text": "Issuance", "bbox": [538.1, 1333.7, 599.2, 1352.2]}, {"text": "Weighted-Average", "bbox": [672.9, 1300.4, 804.1, 1318.9]}, {"text": "Rate at Date of", "bbox": [685.0, 1317.1, 791.9, 1335.5]}, {"text": "Issuance", "bbox": [707.9, 1333.7, 769.0, 1352.2]}, {"text": "Contractual Maturity Date", "bbox": [902.6, 1333.4, 1095.2, 1351.9]}, {"text": "May 2015", "bbox": [249.1, 1360.0, 334.1, 1383.1]}, {"text": "$500,000", "bbox": [529.7, 1360.0, 607.8, 1383.1]}, {"text": "0.88%", "bbox": [711.6, 1360.0, 765.4, 1383.1]}, {"text": "May 2016 - December 2022", "bbox": [881.5, 1360.0, 1116.4, 1383.1]}, {"text": "January 2015", "bbox": [235.8, 1391.3, 347.5, 1414.4]}, {"text": "$700,000", "bbox": [529.7, 1391.3, 607.8, 1414.4]}, {"text": "0.89%", "bbox": [711.6, 1391.3, 765.4, 1414.4]}, {"text": "February 2016 - August 2022", "bbox": [876.3, 1391.3, 1122.7, 1414.4]}, {"text": "April 2014", "bbox": [246.1, 1422.5, 337.0, 1445.6]}, {"text": "$850,000", "bbox": [529.7, 1422.5, 607.8, 1445.6]}, {"text": "0.66%", "bbox": [711.6, 1422.5, 765.4, 1445.6]}, {"text": "April 2015 - October 2021", "bbox": [887.8, 1